✅ Approved the contribution.

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: it can be a good puzzle in shortest or fastest mode

❌ Rejected the contribution.
Comment: visible memory leaks due to recursion

Goal section and Output section
* Please correct the typo "weigth" (a few times, in both sections).
* What do you mean by "volume of weigth"? I suggest it to be simplified as "total weight". (2 times in Goal section) That's also how you describe it in Output section.

Input section and Output section
* You have two "Line 3"s and no "Line 2".
* Please format the line numbers as bold e.g. <<Line 1:>>.
* Please format the variables e.g. [[B]].
* Please specify all variable types (integer, string) in the descriptions.
* Please specify that the exercise type is one of these three: {{bp}}, {{lp}} and {{p}}.

Constraints section
* Can the constraints be omitted? It does not seem they add much to the clash.

Game modes
* It looks impossible in Reverse mode. I suggest to remove it.

Stub generator
* Please add a write statement.

Thanks.
